druids, ranjors, wizzies (ie non- mezz breaking snares, not dot ones!!!) Please snare anything and everything.  Druid ensnare is a beauty, last nearly 10 mins.  Snare doesn’t break mezz, and makes it very easy to remezz.<br>
<br>
